title: Which K-pop idol is always a head turner? - Quora

response.answer_text: there’s six people for me (and to no surprise, most of them are my biases lol). it’s hwang hyunjin, kim doyoung, iu, jung jaehyun, god jihyo, and kim mingyu. i genuinely think most of these idols haven’t had a bad era yet. hyunjin | stray kids - ethereal. he’s handsome and talented and a great dancer and i could honestly go on and on about him. also jyp better not cut his hair or imma throw hands smh        doyoung | nct - idk he always makes clothes… look good? like he could wear a trash bag and somehow style it to look good. he’s so professional and snuggly and i love him lol        iu | soloist. she just seems so peaceful and aesthetic and calm and it gives off queen vibes, no joke.      jaehyun | nct. he just looks good in everything, must i say more?      god jihyo | twice. it’s just something about her that makes you feel some sort of way.        mingyu | seventeen. my man can pull off any concept and look amazing. it’s just the way he holds himself that’s so… powerful? i can’t really explain it, you just know when you see him. maybe it’s the eyebrows.

I'd say Tzuyu.  She is considered a top tier visual in Korea and also internationally. Tzuyu has been loved for her visuals even before the debut of her group. She appeared on the list of ‘most beautiful faces’ five times in a row and won the poll last year becoming the ‘most beautiful face of 2019’. Needless to say, Tzuyu is considered beautiful worldwide and turns heads wherever she goes.  (Here, the photographer is awestruck by her beauty. He seems lost.)  (Even the airport staff is mesmerized by how beautiful Tzuyu is! ) Tzuyu has been a looker throughout her teens as well. According to Jongyeon, guys would approach Tzuyu everytime she'd walk to school. She would receive attention from people even when she's leisurely standing in the subway! Tzuyu is so attractive that even fellow idol can't help but admire her.  (Sojeong says ‘she's pretty'. )  ( Kangnam is awestruck.)  (Naeun thinks Tzuyu is beautiful and shy) Westerners seem to find her gorgeous as well.  Tzuyu was voted by westerners as most beautiful among a list of seven female idols. A candid picture of her at an airport was used here , yet she managed to win. Like, wow! She is certainly a stunner !

I think this goes to Hyunjin (Stray Kids) in my opinion. His talent, charisma, and visuals are always something to admire. (To be honest, I think the whole Stray Kids for that matter.)     But the reason I chose Hyunjin for today’s answer is due to the fact that so many people are mesmerized by his new hair. Apart from Stray Kids’ amazing music and performances, Hyunjin seems to have brought a lot of attention to the group, because of his “long blonde hair”. Ever since (i think) the Psycho performance, people have been asking questions like “omg who’s the guy with the long blonde hair?”     Even when I sent the “Back Door” YT link to my friend, the first thing she asked me was “who’s the guy with the long pink hair? He’s gorgeous!” It’s true, Hyunjin is absolutely gorgeous! However, please do also appreciate the amount of effort and hard work he puts in as a dancer, vocalist, and rapper. He’s extremely talented and an amazing human being, who even has “counseling vlives” where fans share their worries with him and he gives them comfort and or advice.
